          This guide is about <strong>integrated AEO suites</strong> — platforms that combine citation monitoring, content workflow, entity management, and reporting into a single product. If you are assembling a stack from best-in-breed point tools, each chosen for a specific job (schema generation, answer tracking, content analysis), the <a href="/top-aeo-software/" class="text-accent-400 underline decoration-accent-500/30 underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-300">top AEO software guide</a> is the right starting point. This guide evaluates suites and managed platforms: the four platform categories active in 2026, the criteria that separate credible enterprise solutions from superficial dashboards, and a buyer's framework for matching platform scope to programme stage.
        </p>
