        <span class="eyebrow">Vendor Landscape</span>
        <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl font-bold grad-text">Known Vendors by Category</h2>
        <p class="mt-6"><strong>The following vendors are publicly active in the AEO and AI visibility platform space as of mid-2026 — inclusion reflects public market presence, not an endorsement of specific claims or capabilities.</strong></p>
        <p>The AEO platform market divides between purpose-built measurement tools that have extended toward suite features, and established SEO vendors that have built AI visibility modules into existing platforms. Understanding which category a vendor sits in matters, because the depth of workflow integration differs sharply between them.</p>
        <p>In the AI Visibility Measurement Suite category, enterprise-oriented platforms from BrightEdge and Conductor represent the most integrated end of the spectrum — both have added AI answer tracking and citation monitoring to existing suites that already include content workflow, reporting, and account management infrastructure. These platforms are positioned at enterprise scale, with dedicated onboarding and managed service options. Newer measurement-first tools such as Peec.ai, Profound, Goodie AI, and Otterly.AI are strong citation trackers that some buyers use within a broader stack, but they are more accurately described as point tools (see the <a href="/top-aeo-software/" class="text-accent-400 underline decoration-accent-500/30 underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-300">top AEO software guide</a>) rather than full platforms with integrated optimisation workflow.</p>
        <p>For content-layer and retrieval-augmented platforms, Semrush's suite represents the most complete integration of content optimisation, backlink analysis, and AI visibility features under one platform interface. The Semrush content marketing toolkit and AI writing features are accessible within a single account, reducing context-switching for teams. For entity and knowledge graph work at the platform level, Kalicube Pro offers a structured approach to managing entity authority signals that affect AI model understanding — this is the least consolidated category and remains a specialist domain.</p>
        <p>Integrated SEO + AEO suites from Ahrefs and Moz have each released AI visibility features. Buyers should evaluate these specifically by testing actual AI platform coverage breadth and citation granularity in a trial before committing — AEO feature depth varies considerably between platforms even within the same vendor category.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 rounded-lg border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-500/10 p-4 text-sm text-amber-200">
          <strong>Verification note:</strong> Vendor capabilities, pricing, and even market presence change frequently in this space. The vendors named above are publicly known as of the date of this guide. Confirm current feature sets, coverage, and pricing directly before any purchasing decision. GEOoptimised has no affiliate relationship with any named vendor.
